izing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;(RegExp)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 宋体; color: black;&quot;&gt;也可以是字符串&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;(string)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 宋体; color: black;&quot;&gt;，&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;replaceText&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 宋体; color: black;&quot;&gt;是替代查找到的字符串。。为了帮助大家更好的理解，下面举个简单例子说明一下&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px auto; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;Js&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 宋体; color: black;&quot;&gt;代码&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:left;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px auto 10px 0cm; text-indent: -18pt; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;1.&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &amp;#39;Times New Roman&amp;#39;;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;script language=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-s